Texts.Eng: Bring the ^orange;booze kit^reset; to ^green;me^reset; at the ^orange;Science Outpost^reset;
So you want to make your own booze? Great! I'll help you. You must start by crafting a ^green;Booze Kit^white;. Place it against a wall and you can start your path to becoming a Brew Master!
Your path to brewing enlightment has started. Before we really start with the alcohol though, you must first use the Booze Kit to craft the other stations you'll require.
